name: Antilles Maneuver & Rebel Reinforcements
Text: 'USED: Cancel Lateral Damage (Immune to Sense.) OR During opponent''s deploy phase, deploy a Rebel of ability < 3 (except an admiral) aboard your starship from Reserve Deck; reshuffleLOST: Once per game, if opponent has more cards with ability on table than you, draw destiny and retrieve up to that number of Rebels and/or Rebel starships (may take one retrieved card into hand).',
